Package: blitzKrig
Title: Fast Kriging with Kronecker Covariance
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Dean",
           family = "Koch",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dkoch@ualberta.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8849-859X"))
Description: Functions for fitting geostatistical models and kriging with gridded data with spatially separable covariance functions (Kronecker covariance). Kronecker products are used to simplify computations for likelihood, conditional mean, and more.
